✅ PHASE 3 — How Drone Flies
Complete Flight Logic:
W Key Pressed
      ↓
InputThrottle increases
      ↓
CalculateRotorSpeeds()
      ↓
PID_Altitude calculates thrust
      ↓
All 4 rotors get thrust values
FL=352 FR=352 BL=368 BR=368
      ↓
ApplyRotorPhysics()
      ↓
TotalThrust > Gravity (980)
      ↓
Drone lifts UP! 🚁

